				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Mage cannot self heal.  That is the biggest problem with dueling a cleric.  They have those uber efficient heals and just seem to never run OOM, esp with some ele gear and FT15.  Smart clerics:
<br />

<br />
- Reverse Damage shield your pet
<br />
- Melee you down with summoned hammer (you can run, but +50% to their melee range hurts)
<br />
- Dispell the hell out of you
<br />

<br />
With the new PvP resists, Clerics were landing nukes on me with over 300 MR.  I had raid buffs on, but no bard hehe.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1036279&resize=true" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Mattwi Nerfbat</a>
<br />
Arcanist
<br />
Morell-Thule</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
