		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row2"><span class="name"><a name="228514"></a><b>Jaffo</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Magician<br /><br /><br />Joined: 13 Jan 2004<br />Posts: 7<br /></span><br /></td>
