			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Qaedain Magi'kot wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">I am equipped roughly in elemental gear. My opponent cleric was equipped roughly in elemental gear.
<br />

<br />
1. Sic pet.
<br />
2. Dump HoE on him/her as fast as possible
<br />
3. Dispell twice while he/she is dealing with HoE
<br />
4. Debuff while she's dealing with HoE
